<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>

<%- include("includes/head", {title, page, cssPath}) -%>

<body>

<%- include("includes/navbar", navigationLinks) %>

<div class='banner'>
<h1><%= title %></h1>
</div>

<main>

<div class="welcome">
<div class="welcome_text">
<p><%= greeting %></p>
<p>We are Linda (24, Germany) and Santi (27, Argentina). We are both EU citizens and speak English fluently, apart from German and Spanish. At the moment (<%= date %>) we are in <%= where %>.</p>
</div>

<figure class="welcome_figure">
<img 
src="<%= mainImg %>" 
alt="Picture of Linda and Santi"
/>
<figcaption>Ischia, 2021</figcaption>
<figure>

</div>

<section id="firstSec" class="firstSec">
<h2><%= firstSec %></h2>
<p>Although the internet brings the distant close, reading isn't the same as first-hand experiences. We have both been volunteering on and off for the last few years after finishing university, where we studied Chemistry (Santi) and Social Sciences (Linda), and spent several years living in the UK.</p>

<p>We like getting to know new places and cultures, people and ideas. We are interested in sustainability and enjoy learning new building and gardening skills. We love spending time in nature and doing various activities such as running, swimming, yoga and meditation. Santi is interested in everything related to technology and Linda loves cooking; it would be great to evolve these skills while volunteering.
</p>
</section>

<section class="secondSec" id="secondSec" >

<h2><%= secondSec %></h2>
<p> In 2021, we have been involved in: </p>

<div class="taskImgFlex">
<ul class="tasks">
<li>Building wooden fences and doors w/ recycled material</li>
<li>Painting & limewashing</li>
<li>Cooking</li>
<li>Gardening, permaculture, Hugelkultur, Charles Dowdings' no-dig approach</li>
<li>Using power tools: chainsaw, miter and circular saw, strimmer</li>
<li>Changeovers and reception at hostels</li>
<li>Basic repairs, IT help </li>
</ul>

<figure class="roundFig" >
<img class="roundFig_img" src="/images/Making_a_door_from_recycled_wood.jpg" alt="Making a door from recycled wood"/>
<figcaption>Door made from recycled wood</figcaption>
</figure>
</div> 

<p class='blueBox'>Check out our <a href='/pictures'>pictures</a>  to see some of the things we've done.</p>

<h3>Places we've worked in</h3>
<ul class="places">
<li><a href="<%= hosts.cotna.url %>"><%= hosts.cotna.aname %></a> <%= hosts.cotna.plus %> (<%= hosts.cotna.howLong %>), <%= hosts.cotna.area %>.
</li>
<li><a href="<%= hosts.jonathan.url %>"><%= hosts.jonathan.aname %></a> <%= hosts.jonathan.plus %> (<%= hosts.jonathan.howLong %>), <%= hosts.jonathan.area %>. <span class='reviewSpan'>See Review</span><img class='reviewImg' src='reviews/jonathan.png'/>
</li>
<li><a href="<%= hosts.skye.url %>"><%= hosts.skye.aname %></a> <%= hosts.skye.plus %> (<%= hosts.skye.howLong %>), <%= hosts.skye.area %>.  <span class='reviewSpan' >See Review</span> <img class='reviewImg' src='reviews/skye.png'/>
</li>
<li><a href="<%= hosts.bosavern.url %>"><%= hosts.bosavern.aname %></a> <%= hosts.bosavern.plus %> (<%= hosts.bosavern.howLong %>), <%= hosts.bosavern.area %>.
</li>


</ul>
<h3>Heads up!</h3>
<p class="quoteLikePar">
We are now looking for new destinations in Europe<span style="font-size:2rem; color:red; font-weight:bold">!!!</span> Get in touch using the links below, or drop us an email at <a href="mailto:santi+linda@pm.me&subject=Volunteering">santi+linda@pm.me</a>.</p>
</section>

